	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus in domino Iesu.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8093">Hercules</persName> te salvere iubet, me autem rogavit, ut tibi nota facerem, quae nuper in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> acciderunt.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Arx quaedam est sive, ut <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Itali</placeName> aiunt, fortalicium inexpugnabile inter <persName ref="p8088" cert="high">Regium</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name">Mutinam</persName>, quae opida sunt <persName type="citizen_name">ducis Ferrarie</persName>, situm, quod ipse dux maxima cura custodiri semper voluit, a <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolano</placeName> distans miliaribus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanicis</placeName> viginti vel circa.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux <persName type="auto_name">Florentinus</persName> consentiente papa, quoniam<note type="misc">qm</note> et ipse est de domo Medica, huiusmodi arcem cum maximo omnium stupore proditione facta ab eo, qui loci illius curam habebat, cepit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Indicat autem <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8093">Hercules</persName> bellorum peritus rem hanc <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italie</placeName> magnorum motuum causam fore; nam <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetis</placeName>, qui cum <placeName ref="l150" cert="high">Ferrariensi</placeName> duce confederati sunt, magno detrimento erit, nedum ipsi duci.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam facile erit <persName ref="p8088" cert="high">Regium</persName> et Mutinam aggredi et ab inimicis capi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti ipsum ducem quotannis ob eas civitates pendere pape tributum magnum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si hec duo opida caperentur, <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetis</placeName> magna pericula imminerent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Estimat autem <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8093">Hercules</persName> id consentiente etiam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18575" cert="high">Philippo</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniarum</placeName> rege, qui <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetis</placeName> infensus est, factum fuisse, merces digna profecto cardinali <placeName ref="l150" cert="high">Ferrariensi</placeName>, qui antichristi in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> partes tuetur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Diebus praeteritis aliquot armatorum milia nomine pape, que Avenionem mittenda erant, <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolano</placeName>, ubi congregata erant, discesserunt <placeName ref="l55" cert="high">Bononiam</placeName> versus, nonnulli dicebant mare versus iter arripuisse.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videmus nunc, quid machinate sint vulpes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc te scire voluimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l93" cert="high">Clavene</placeName> 4. augusti 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p2019" cert="high">Augustinus Mainardus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eximio viro domino <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabricio</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensi</placeName> pastori, semper observando.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curie</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Unter dem Text Zusatz von <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8009">Fabricius</persName> (an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>):]</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Glychs ist h. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8114">Balinket</persName> ouch von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l36" cert="high">Pergama</placeName> zuͦgeschriben und die veste genennt, namlich <placeName type="auto_name">Rübera</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Bald ist anders schryben ouch dodannen kommen, es sölle nitt syn, und züche des baapst volckh uff <placeName ref="l1121" cert="high">Genuam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In bellis multa inania; sed mirum, quis tales rumores serat aut in quem finem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnes, qui ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> veniunt, constanter affirman[t] <placeName type="citizen_name">Riberam</placeName> proditione captam.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc quid verum, quid vanum sit, difficile dictu est.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
